OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774552271
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police officers
OL,4,Cunder investigation following man's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThree Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,8,Fofficers are under investigation for
OL,9,Fgross misconduct after a man died in
OL,10,Fpolice custody.
OL,12,FOn 15 January Michael Carolan fell ill
OL,13,Fwhile in custody at Torquay police
OL,14,Fstation. He died at 5am after being
OL,15,Ftransferred to hospital by ambulance.
OL,17,FMr Carolan had been reported missing
OL,18,Fby concerned family members at 9pm the
OL,19,Fprevious evening and was found by
OL,20,Fofficers in Paignton just less than an
OL,21,Fhour later.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
