FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774552271
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police officers
OL,4,Cunder investigation following man's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe 28-year-old was arrested and taken
OL,8,Fto Torquay police station.
OL,10,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,11,FConduct (IOPC) said they received a
OL,12,Freferral from the force soon after Mr
OL,13,FCarolan's death.
OL,15,FThey explained how their investigation
OL,16,Fwill examine all the circumstances in
OL,17,Fthe build-up to Mr Carolan's death.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774552271
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police officers
OL,4,Cunder investigation following man's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThis includes the decision to arrest,
OL,8,Fthe nature and adequacy of searches
OL,9,Fcarried out and the medical attention
OL,10,Fhe received.
OL,12,FThey will review CCTV and body worn
OL,13,Ffootage and gather accounts from
OL,14,Fofficers and staff involved in his
OL,15,Farrest and detention.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774552271
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police officers
OL,4,Cunder investigation following man's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThey went on to say: "We have notified
OL,8,Fthree police officers that they are
OL,9,Funder gross misconduct investigation
OL,10,Ffor possible breaches of police
OL,11,Fprofessional standards regarding
OL,12,Fauthority, respect and courtesy and
OL,13,Fduties and responsibilities.
OL,15,F"The notices relate to their
OL,16,Finteractions with Mr Carolan and the
OL,17,Fchecks carried out on him during his
OL,18,Fdetention. This will be kept under
OL,19,Freview throughout our enquiries."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
