OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774552271
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police officers
OL,4,Cunder investigation following man's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FIOPC Director, Derrick Campbell said:
OL,8,F"My sympathies are with Mr Carolan's
OL,9,Ffamily and friends and everyone
OL,10,Faffected by his death."
OL,12,FHe added: "We are independent of the
OL,13,Fpolice and it is important that we
OL,14,Fcarry out an investigation to fully
OL,15,Festablish the circumstances when
OL,16,Fsomeone has died in police custody."
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@KOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
