OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774552271
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police officers
OL,4,Cunder investigation following man's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FIPOC stressed that the serving of
OL,8,Fgross misconduct notices does not mean
OL,9,Fthat disciplinary proceedings will
OL,10,Ffollow and that decisions on whether
OL,11,For not disciplinary proceedings should
OL,12,Ftake place will be taken at the end of
OL,13,Ftheir investigation.
OL,15,FThey say they are also looking at a
OL,16,Fcomplaint from Mr Carolan's family in
OL,17,Frelation to how police communicated
OL,18,Fwith them during his detention and
OL,19,Fafter he died.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
